This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new loss function for deep neural network classification. It also involves training criteria and performance evaluation, which are common topics in machine learning research. Additionally, the paper focuses on image classification tasks, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category. Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as they are also related to deep learning and classification tasks.
